    {
      "name": "Red Barrel",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>If this demon is killed by a firearm or explosive, or hit by a flamethrower at all, it will explode. The explosion is mechanically similar to dynamite or a grenade (pg.72), except all within the affected area also have the chance to catch fire. A TN 6 Prowess save is required to avoid this.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
