    },
    {
      "name": "Furnace",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>When threatened, this demon automatically increases its heat output. This can get to so high a temperature that it can actually burn other characters. If any character or demon, excluding other demons of the same type, spends more than 3 turns in combat with this demon in an enclosed space, at the beginning of their following turn and every turn after, they will take a 3/W3 Wound. For every additional demon of this type present, increase the damage by 1. For every third demon of this type present, increase the Wound severity by 1.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
      },
      "_id": "0zJQWAaJEfc4ziHA",
      "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
      "_key": "!actors.items!61he2BLfblUaVlkE.0zJQWAaJEfc4ziHA"
    },
    {
      "name": "Thick Skin",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>This demon has a very thick dermal layer which reduces the damage and severity of any Wound taken by 1.</p>",
        "action": "passive"
      },
      "_id": "O1DWvqeycg59sAdB",
      "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
      "_key": "!actors.items!61he2BLfblUaVlkE.O1DWvqeycg59sAdB"
    },
    {
      "name": "Spit",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon spits a wad of saliva at a target. This attack does no damage, but if hit the target will be covered in a thick coat of extremely flammable saliva. Saving throws to avoid catching fire increase to TN 7. During combat it can be removed by spending a Full action to do so before it catches fire.</p>",
        "action": "major"
      },
